--Query----------
INSERT INTO SERVICE_REQUEST(CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,REQ_TIME) VALUES ('1041','Pest Control Service','Too many cockroaches.',TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-04 22:52:11','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'));
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-04 22:52:11','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-04 22:52:11','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =1041ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-04 22:52:11','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID, O.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID AND S.CUSTOMER_ID =1041 ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID FROM CUSTOMER WHERE PHONE_NUMBER='01926422351' AND PASSWORD='HelloEveryone'
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT WORKER_ID FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE PHONE_NUMBER='01926422351' AND PASSWORD='HelloEveryone'
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 41
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=41;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 41
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=41;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =41),41,61);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 61)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 61;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=41;
--EndQuery-------

            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),
            TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=41;
--EndQuery-------

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-05 00:01:05','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-05 00:01:05','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =1041ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-05 00:01:05','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;

                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=65)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=65;

                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 65) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=65)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=65;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 65) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 UPDATE GROUP_PEST_CONTROL 
                                        SET WORKER_ID = 65 WHERE ORDER_ID = 101;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
												FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
												WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=65))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=65)

												;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=65))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=65)

            												;

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID FROM CUSTOMER WHERE PHONE_NUMBER='01710000001' AND PASSWORD='HelloEveryone'
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT WORKER_ID FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE PHONE_NUMBER='01710000001' AND PASSWORD='HelloEveryone'
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 82
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=82)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=82)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=82;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 82) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =82),82,103);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 103)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 103;
--EndQuery-------

            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID

                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=83)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=83;

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID

            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 83) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
												FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
												WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=83))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=83)

												;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=83))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=83)

            												;

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 87
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=87)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=87)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=87;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 87) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =87),87,105);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 105)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 105;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 INSERT INTO GROUP_FORM(ORDER_ID, GROUP_SIZE, TEAM_LEADER_ID)
        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 105 ), 0, 87);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 87
--EndQuery-------

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=87)

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
												FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
												WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=82))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=82)

												;
--EndQuery-------

                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=82))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=82)

            												;

--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

             SELECT	o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
             
             FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
             
             WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 1061
             AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
             AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NOT NULL;
             
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

--EndQuery-------

INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =82),82,107);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 107)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 107;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 INSERT INTO GROUP_FORM(ORDER_ID, GROUP_SIZE, TEAM_LEADER_ID)
        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 107 ), 0, 82);
--EndQuery-------

            AND s.WORKER_ID=84;
--EndQuery-------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 84) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID);

            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=82)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=82)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=82;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 82) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =82),82,121);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 121)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 121;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 INSERT INTO GROUP_FORM(ORDER_ID, GROUP_SIZE, TEAM_LEADER_ID)
        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 121 ), 0, 82);
--EndQuery-------

            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=82)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=82)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=82;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 82) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
												FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
												WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=82))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=82)

												;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O, GROUP_FORM g
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=82))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=82)
                            AND O.ORDER_ID = g.ORDER_ID
                            AND g.GROUP_SIZE = 2
                            AND O.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NULL;
--EndQuery-------

                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=83)

             SELECT	o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
             
             FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
             
             WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 1061
             AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
             AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NOT NULL;
             
--EndQuery-------

                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID

                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2

            AND s.WORKER_ID=41;

            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=41)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=41;
--EndQuery-------

            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=64)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=64)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=64;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO SERVICE_REQUEST(CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,REQ_TIME) VALUES ('1041','Pest Control Service','Lots of Ants.',TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-06 23:41:05','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'));
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-06 23:41:06','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-06 23:41:06','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =1041ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-06 23:41:06','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID, O.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID AND S.CUSTOMER_ID =1041 ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =65),65,81);

UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 81)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 81;

                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 65) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=65)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=65)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=65;
--EndQuery-------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 65) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID);

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
												FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
												WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=65))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=65)

												;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=65))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=65)

            												;
--EndQuery-------

            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=81)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=81)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=81;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 81) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
												FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
												WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1450))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1450)

												;

                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2

            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1463)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=1463;

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID

            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1463)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1463)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=1463;
--EndQuery-------

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID

            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1463) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID);

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1463)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1463)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=1463;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1463) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
												FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
												WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1463))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1463)

												;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1463))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1463)

            												;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1450)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1450)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=1450;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1450) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1450))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1450)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 1450;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O

                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1450))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1450)

            												;
--EndQuery-------

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 03:32:54','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 03:32:54','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =3052ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 03:32:54','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O  
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND O.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NULL  
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 3052 
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
                    
--EndQuery-------

             SELECT	o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
             
             FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
             
             WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 3052
             AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
             AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NOT NULL;
             
--EndQuery-------

                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID
                    AND O.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NULL
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID =3052 ORDER BY O.START_TIME;

            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1450)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1450)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=1450;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1450) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1450))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1450)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 1450;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O, GROUP_FORM g
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1450))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1450)
                            AND O.ORDER_ID = g.ORDER_ID
                            AND g.GROUP_SIZE = 2
                            AND O.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NULL;
--EndQuery-------

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 17:49:31','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 17:49:31','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =3052ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 17:49:31','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;

--Query----------

             SELECT	o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
             
             FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
             
             WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 3052
             AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
             AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NOT NULL;
             
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O  
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND O.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NULL  
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 3052 
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1463) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =1463),1463,84);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 84)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 84;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 INSERT INTO GROUP_FORM(ORDER_ID, GROUP_SIZE, TEAM_LEADER_ID)
        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 84 ), 0, 1463);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1463
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1463)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1463 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=1463))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=1463;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1463) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME || ' ' || LAST_NAME,TYPE,PHONE_NUMBER,TO_CHAR(DATE_OF_BIRTH,'DL'),THANA_NAME,RATING FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1463
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 17:51:03','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 17:51:03','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =3052ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 17:51:03','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

             SELECT	o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
             
             FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
             
             WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 3052
             AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
             AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NOT NULL;
             
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O  
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND O.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NULL  
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 3052 
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1474)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=1474 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=1474))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=1474;

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1474) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID);

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1474))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1474)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 1474;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O, GROUP_FORM g
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1474))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1474)
                            AND O.ORDER_ID = g.ORDER_ID
                            AND g.GROUP_SIZE = 2
                            AND O.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NULL;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1474))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1474)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 1474;

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 20:37:12','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 20:37:12','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =3458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 20:37:12','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

             SELECT	o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
             
             FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
             
             WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 3458
             AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
             AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NOT NULL;
             
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O  
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND O.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NULL  
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 3458 
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 20:38:49','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 20:38:49','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =3458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 20:38:49','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

             SELECT	o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
             
             FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
             
             WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 3458
             AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
             AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID
             AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NOT NULL;
             
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O  
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND O.TEAM_LEADER_ID IS NULL  
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 3458 
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 3458

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1674) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1674))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1674)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 1674;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O, GROUP_FORM g
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1674))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=1674)
                            AND O.ORDER_ID = g.ORDER_ID
                            AND g.GROUP_SIZE = 2
                            AND g.CUSTOMER_APPROVED = 1;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 1674
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID FROM CUSTOMER WHERE PHONE_NUMBER='01810000388' AND PASSWORD='cse388'
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT WORKER_ID FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE PHONE_NUMBER='01810000388' AND PASSWORD='cse388'
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER_ID = 4458
--EndQuery-------

--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 21:59:39','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 21:59:39','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =4458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 21:59:39','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 4458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 4458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER_ID = 4458
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=2174)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=2174 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=2174))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=2174;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 2174) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =2174),2174,94);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 94)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 94;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 INSERT INTO GROUP_FORM(ORDER_ID, GROUP_SIZE, TEAM_LEADER_ID)
        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 94 ), 0, 2174);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 2174
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=2174)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=2174 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=2174))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=2174;
--EndQuery-------

                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=2175)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=2175 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=2175))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=2175;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 2175) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2175))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2175)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 2175;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O, GROUP_FORM g
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2175))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2175)
                            AND O.ORDER_ID = g.ORDER_ID
                            AND g.GROUP_SIZE = 2
                            AND g.CUSTOMER_APPROVED = 1;

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:06:11','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:06:11','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =4458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:06:11','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 4458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 4458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:06:21','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:06:21','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =4458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:06:21','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 4458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 4458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

        UPDATE ORDER_INFO
        SET START_TIME = SYSTIMESTAMP

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2174))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2174)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 2174;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                        SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                        FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O, GROUP_FORM g
                        WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2174))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2174)
                            AND O.ORDER_ID = g.ORDER_ID
                            AND g.GROUP_SIZE = 2
                            AND g.CUSTOMER_APPROVED = 1;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

        UPDATE ORDER_INFO
        SET END_TIME = SYSTIMESTAMP
        WHERE ORDER_ID = 48;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2174))

                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2174)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 2174;

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 4458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 4458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=2374)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=2374)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=2374;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 2374) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2174))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2174)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 2174;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=2174)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;
