--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3046)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3046 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3046))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3046;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3046) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =3046),3046,103);
--EndQuery-------

                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 103)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 103;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3046)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3046 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3046))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3046;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3046) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:44:36','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:44:36','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =5458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:44:36','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            DECLARE
            ID NUMBER;
            BEGIN
                SELECT WORKER_ID INTO ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE ORDER_ID=50;
                CALCRATING(3,ID,'WORKER');
            END ;
            
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:44:41','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:44:41','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =5458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:44:41','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3003)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3003 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3003))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3003;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3003) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID

INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =2874),2874,101);

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 101)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 101;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 INSERT INTO GROUP_FORM(ORDER_ID, GROUP_SIZE, TEAM_LEADER_ID)
        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 101 ), 0, 2874);

                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3003)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3003 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3003))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3003;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3003) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3003))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3003)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3003;
--EndQuery-------

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:47:26','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:47:26','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =5458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:47:26','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:47:29','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:47:29','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =5458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-09 22:47:29','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3074))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3074)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3074;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                            FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3074))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3074)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;
--EndQuery-------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

            ID NUMBER;
            BEGIN
                SELECT WORKER_ID INTO ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE ORDER_ID=52;
                CALCRATING(3,ID,'WORKER');
            END ;
            
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=2874)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=2874 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=2874))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=2874;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 2874) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =2874),2874,106);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 106)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 106;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 INSERT INTO GROUP_FORM(ORDER_ID, GROUP_SIZE, TEAM_LEADER_ID)
        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 106 ), 0, 2874);
--EndQuery-------

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf

                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3046)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3046 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3046))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3046;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3046) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3046))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3046)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3046;
--EndQuery-------

                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR

                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3003)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3003 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3003))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3003;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3003) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3003))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3003)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3003;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                            FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3003))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3003)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID FROM CUSTOMER WHERE PHONE_NUMBER='01810000388' AND PASSWORD='cse388'
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT WORKER_ID FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE PHONE_NUMBER='01810000388' AND PASSWORD='cse388'
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
--EndQuery-------

--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID

            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);

                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;

                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 5458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3774)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3774)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=3774;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3774) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3774)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3774)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=3774;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3774) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3774))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3774)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3774;
--EndQuery-------

                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3574))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3574;
--EndQuery-------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3574) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR

                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL

                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3574;

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3574))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3574;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3574) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3574))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3574)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3574;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                            FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3574))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3574)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;
--EndQuery-------

            DECLARE
            ID NUMBER;
            BEGIN
                SELECT WORKER_ID INTO ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE ORDER_ID=55;
                CALCRATING(3,ID,'WORKER');
            END ;
            
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 00:30:42','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 00:30:42','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =6458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 00:30:42','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3574))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3574;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3574) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3574
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3574))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3574;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3574) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3574))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3574)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3574;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3574) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID);

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3703)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3703 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3703))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3703;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3703) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3703))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3703)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3703;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 3703 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=3703)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 3703
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                            FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3703))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3703)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;
--EndQuery-------

            DECLARE
            ID NUMBER;
            BEGIN
                SELECT CUSTOMER_ID INTO ID FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID=55;
                CALCRATING(3,ID,'CUSTOMER');
            END ;
            
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3703))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3703)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3703;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 3703 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=3703)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 3703
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3703)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;

SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3574))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3574;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3574) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3574))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3574)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3574;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 3574 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=3574)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 3574
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT

                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3703)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3703 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3703))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3703;

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3703) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =3703),3703,121);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 121)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 121;
--EndQuery-------

        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 121 ), 0, 3703);

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3574))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3574)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3574;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 3574 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=3574)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 3574
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:05:27','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:05:27','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =6458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:05:27','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:05:30','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:05:30','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =6458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:05:30','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3703))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3703)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3703;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 3703 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=3703)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 3703
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:08:24','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:08:24','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =6458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:08:24','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3574 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3574))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=3574;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3574) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=3746 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=3746))

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 3746) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3746))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3746)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 3746;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 3746 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=3746)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 3746
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                            FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3746))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=3746)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

--EndQuery-------

--EndQuery-------

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:11:31','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:11:31','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =6458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 18:11:31','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 6458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 22:05:11','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 22:05:11','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =7458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 22:05:11','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4581)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4581)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=4581;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 4581) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID); 
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =4581),4581,124);
--EndQuery-------

UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 124)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 124;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 124 ), 0, 4581);
--EndQuery-------

                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4981)

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 4981) = ANY( SELECT TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID);

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4981))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4981)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4981;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 4981 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=4981)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 4981
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4981)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 22:07:25','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 22:07:25','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =7458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 22:07:25','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 22:07:28','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 22:07:28','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =7458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-10 22:07:28','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.TEAM_LEADER_ID = ANY( SELECT TEAM_LEADER_ID FROM GROUP_FORM WHERE CUSTOMER_APPROVED=0);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
