--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4581)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4581)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=4581;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4581) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4581 AND gf.WORKER_ID!=4581 AND gf.WORKER_ID_2 != 4581 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4581);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 4581
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4581)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4581)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=4581;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4581) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4581 AND gf.WORKER_ID!=4581 AND gf.WORKER_ID_2 != 4581 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4581);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4581;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 4581 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=4581)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 4581
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                            FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;
--EndQuery-------

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4581)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4581)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=4581;
--EndQuery-------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4581) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4581 AND gf.WORKER_ID!=4581 AND gf.WORKER_ID_2 != 4581 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4581);

                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581))

                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4581;

            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID

        SET START_TIME = SYSTIMESTAMP
        WHERE ORDER_ID = 62;

                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4581;

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 4581 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=4581)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 4581
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                            FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

--Query----------
             
            SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
            WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4581)
            AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4581)
            AND s.WORKER_ID=4581;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4581) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4581 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4581 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4581 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4581);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4581;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 4581 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=4581)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 4581
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4581))

                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4581;

            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID

            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp,GROUP_FORM GF
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND GF.CUSTOMER_APPROVED = 0;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;

SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,NVL(c.RATING,0),a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4281))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4281;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4281) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4281 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4281);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =4281),4281,127);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 127)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 127;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 INSERT INTO GROUP_FORM(ORDER_ID, GROUP_SIZE, TEAM_LEADER_ID)
        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 127 ), 0, 4281);
--EndQuery-------

SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,NVL(c.RATING,0),a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4281))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4281;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4281) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4281 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4281);
--EndQuery-------

                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4410)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4410 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4410))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4410;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4410) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4410 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4410 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4410 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4410);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4410;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 4410 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=4410)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 4410
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp,GROUP_FORM GF

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;

--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

            BEGIN
            REJECT_GROUP_REQUEST(64);
            END;
            /

SELECT CUSTOMER_ID FROM CUSTOMER WHERE PHONE_NUMBER='01910000001' AND PASSWORD='Elec1'

SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 4281

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,NVL(c.RATING,0),a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4281))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4281;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4281) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4281 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4281);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =4281),4281,128);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 128)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 128;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 INSERT INTO GROUP_FORM(ORDER_ID, GROUP_SIZE, TEAM_LEADER_ID)
        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 128 ), 0, 4281);
--EndQuery-------

SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,NVL(c.RATING,0),a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4410)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4410 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4410))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4410;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4410) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4410 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4410 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4410 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4410);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4410;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 4410 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=4410)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 4410
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                            FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;

                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4453 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4453))

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4453) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4453 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4453 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4453 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4453);

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4453))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4453)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4453;

            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID

            AND S.WORKER_ID = 4453

            ;

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp,GROUP_FORM GF
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND GF.CUSTOMER_APPROVED = 0;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

            END;

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,NVL(c.RATING,0),a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4281))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4281;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND (SELECT sp1.TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER sp1 WHERE sp1.WORKER_ID = 4281) = ANY( SELECT sp.TYPE FROM GROUP_FORM g, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp WHERE g.TEAM_LEADER_ID = sp.WORKER_ID)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4281 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4281);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO ORDER_INFO(TYPE, WORKER_ID,REQUEST_NO)
                                VALUES( (SELECT TYPE
                                FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER
                                WHERE WORKER_ID =4281),4281,127);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
UPDATE SERVICE_REQUEST
                SET ORDER_ID = (SELECT ORDER_ID
                FROM ORDER_INFO
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 127)
                WHERE REQUEST_NO = 127;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
 INSERT INTO GROUP_FORM(ORDER_ID, GROUP_SIZE, TEAM_LEADER_ID)
        VALUES( (SELECT ORDER_ID FROM ORDER_INFO WHERE REQUEST_NO = 127 ), 0, 4281);
--EndQuery-------

                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4410)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4410 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4410))

            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,NVL(c.RATING,0),a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4410)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4410 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4410))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4410;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND a.TYPE = (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 4410)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4410 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4410 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4410 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4410);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4410;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,
            C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,
            ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 4410 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=4410)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 4410
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                            FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4410)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-11 16:39:45','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-11 16:39:45','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =7458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-11 16:39:45','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp,GROUP_FORM GF
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND GF.CUSTOMER_APPROVED = 0;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp,GROUP_FORM GF

            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND GF.CUSTOMER_APPROVED = 0;

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458

--Query----------
SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,NVL(c.RATING,0),a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4281))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4281;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND a.TYPE = (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 4281)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4281 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4281);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4281))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4281)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4281;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 4281 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=4281)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 4281
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME
                            FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O
                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4281))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4281)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;

SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,NVL(c.RATING,0),a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4281))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4281;
--EndQuery-------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND a.TYPE = (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 4281)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4281 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4281);
--EndQuery-------

SELECT c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,c.PHONE_NUMBER,c.ADDRESS,NVL(c.RATING,0),a.DESCRIPTION,a.REQ_TIME, TIMEDIFF2( SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2(SYSTIMESTAMP, a.REQ_TIME, 'min') , a.REQUEST_NO
                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4281))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4281;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND a.TYPE = (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 4281)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4281 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4281);
--EndQuery-------

                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281)

                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4281))

                FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a
                WHERE c.THANA_NAME= s.THANA_NAME
                AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT a2.CUSTOMER_ID
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281)
                AND a.CUSTOMER_ID = c.CUSTOMER_ID
                AND a.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT a2.REQUEST_NO
                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST a2,SERVICE_PROVIDER s2
                                        WHERE a2.Order_id IS NULL AND LOWER(a2.TYPE)= LOWER(s2.TYPE) AND s2.WORKER_ID=4281 AND a2.APPLIANCES_ID = ANY(SELECT APPLIANCES_ID FROM AREA_OF_EXPERTISE WHERE WORKER_ID=4281))
                AND s.WORKER_ID=4281;

--Query----------

            SELECT s.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || s.LAST_NAME AS NAME, c.FIRST_NAME || ' ' ||c.LAST_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, c.PHONE_NUMBER, c.ADDRESS AS CUSTOMER_ADDRESS, a.DESCRIPTION, gf.ORDER_ID
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_PROVIDER s,SERVICE_REQUEST a, GROUP_FORM gf
            WHERE s.WORKER_ID = gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = a.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND a.ORDER_ID = gf.ORDER_ID
            AND a.TYPE = (SELECT TYPE FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 4281)
            AND gf.GROUP_SIZE < 2 
            AND gf.TEAM_LEADER_ID != 4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID,0)!=4281 AND NVL(gf.WORKER_ID_2,0) != 4281 AND s.THANA_NAME = (SELECT THANA_NAME FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID =4281);
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
                FROM CUSTOMER C,ORDER_INFO O,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
                WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4281))
                AND O.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NOT NULL AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL
                AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4281)
                AND S.WORKER_ID = 4281;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,OI.ORDER_ID,OI.START_TIME,OI.END_TIME,ROUND((s.PAYMENT_PER_HOUR*TIMEDIFF2(OI.END_TIME,OI.START_TIME,'sec'))/3600,2)
            FROM GROUP_FORM GF,ORDER_INFO OI,CUSTOMER C, SERVICE_REQUEST SR,SERVICE_PROVIDER S
            WHERE OI.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND SR.ORDER_ID=OI.ORDER_ID
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID=SR.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND OI.TEAM_LEADER_ID = GF.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND (GF.WORKER_ID = 4281 OR GF.WORKER_ID_2=4281)
            AND S.WORKER_ID = 4281
            AND OI.START_TIME IS NOT NULL AND OI.END_TIME IS NOT NULL
            ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT C.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || C.LAST_NAME AS NAME,C.PHONE_NUMBER,C.ADDRESS,O.ORDER_ID,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME

                            WHERE C.CUSTOMER_ID = ANY(SELECT SR.CUSTOMER_ID
                                                                        FROM SERVICE_REQUEST SR
                                                                        WHERE SR.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4281))
                            AND O.ORDER_ID IS NOT NULL AND O.END_TIME IS NULL
                            AND O.REQUEST_NO = ANY(SELECT O.REQUEST_NO FROM ORDER_INFO O WHERE O.WORKER_ID=4281)
                            AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID)=1;
--EndQuery-------

--EndQuery-------

SELECT FIRST_NAME || ' ' || LAST_NAME,TYPE,PHONE_NUMBER,TO_CHAR(DATE_OF_BIRTH,'DL'),THANA_NAME,RATING,RATED_BY FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID = 4281
--EndQuery-------

--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-11 16:45:38','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-11 16:45:38','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =7458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-11 16:45:38','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp,GROUP_FORM GF
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND GF.CUSTOMER_APPROVED = 0;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME || ' ' || LAST_NAME,PHONE_NUMBER,TO_CHAR(DATE_OF_BIRTH,'DL'),THANA_NAME,RATING,RATED_BY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT FIRST_NAME FROM CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
INSERT INTO IN_AN_EMERGENCY(EMERGENCY_TYPE,CUSTOMER_ID) VALUES('Police',7458)
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT IAE.EMERGENCY_TYPE,EPN.PHONE_NUMBER,EPN.THANA_NAME
            FROM IN_AN_EMERGENCY IAE,EMERGENCY_PHONE_NUMBER EPN,CUSTOMER C
            WHERE EPN.THANA_NAME = C.THANA_NAME
            AND IAE.EMERGENCY_TYPE = EPN.EMERGENCY_TYPE
            AND C.CUSTOMER_ID = IAE.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND IAE.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------
SELECT CUSTOMER_ID,TYPE,DESCRIPTION,TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-11 17:00:43','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'HR'),TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-11 17:00:43','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min')FROM SERVICE_REQUEST WHERE ORDER_ID IS NULL AND CUSTOMER_ID =7458ORDER BY TIMEDIFF2( TO_TIMESTAMP('2020-12-11 17:00:43','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), REQ_TIME, 'min') ;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

            SELECT o.ORDER_ID, sp.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || sp.LAST_NAME AS NAME, sp.TYPE, sp.PHONE_NUMBER
            FROM CUSTOMER c, SERVICE_REQUEST sr, ORDER_INFO o, SERVICE_PROVIDER sp,GROUP_FORM GF
            WHERE c.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
            AND c.CUSTOMER_ID = sr.CUSTOMER_ID
            AND sr.ORDER_ID = o.ORDER_ID
            AND sp.WORKER_ID = o.TEAM_LEADER_ID
            AND o.ORDER_ID = GF.ORDER_ID
            AND GF.CUSTOMER_APPROVED = 0;
--EndQuery-------

--Query----------

                    SELECT S.CUSTOMER_ID, S.ORDER_ID,O.TYPE,O.START_TIME,O.END_TIME,ROUND((SELECT PAYMENT_PER_HOUR FROM SERVICE_PROVIDER WHERE WORKER_ID=O.WORKER_ID)*TIMEDIFF2(O.END_TIME,O.START_TIME,'sec')/3600,2) AS PAYMENT
                    FROM SERVICE_REQUEST S, ORDER_INFO O
                    WHERE S.ORDER_ID = O.ORDER_ID  
                    AND CHECK_GROUP_EXISTS_AND_APPROVED(O.ORDER_ID) = 1
                    AND S.CUSTOMER_ID = 7458
                    ORDER BY O.START_TIME;
--EndQuery-------
